movies.title: Operation Finale
movies.plot: In 1960, a team of Israeli secret agents is deployed to find Adolf Eichmann, the infamous Nazi architect of the Holocaust, supposedly hidden in Argentina, and get him to Israel to be judged.

events.title: Adolf Eichmann is captured in Buenos Aires
Adolf Eichmann is flown out of Buenos Aires to Israel

movies.title: Seberg
movies.plot: An ambitious young FBI agent is assigned to investigate iconic actress Jean Seberg when she becomes embroiled in the tumultuous civil rights movement in late 1960s Los Angeles.
